         <div xml:id="main">
            <head type="incipit">
               <supplied reason="XTF-compatibility">Melbourne botan Garden, ¶ 12/10/70 ¶ Sir ¶  ¶ In reference to the proposed reduction of the employees of the botanic Garden, I have the honor of submitting a list, containing those still engaged here ...</supplied>
            </head>
            <p rend="number" xml:lang="en">70.10.12<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; "/>
            </p>
            <p rend="correspondent" xml:lang="en">To James McCulloch</p>
            <p rend="location" xml:lang="en">W70/13816, unit 468, VPRS 3991/P inward registered correspondence VA 475 Chief Secretary's Department, Public Record Office, Victoria.</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn0" n="1">
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">Trans. Angela. To proof.</seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; ">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Is the list there?</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                  </p>
                  <p rend="FootnoteText"
                     style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                     xml:lang="en">
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">I can't see one; there is a list at<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">70-05-11f</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">, but later</seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">
                        <space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
                     </seg>
                     <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="font-weight: bold; color: #C00000; ">one not found</seg>
                  </p>
               </note>Melbourne botan Garden,</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; text-align: end; "
               xml:lang="en">12/10/70</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">Sir</p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>In reference to the proposed reduction of the employees of the botanic Garden, I have the honor of submitting a list, containing those still engaged here with a statement of their length of service and the duties allotted to them. I have also the honor to remark, that their work in their different portions is so varied, as to render a reduction according to juniority an impossibility<seg rend="FootnoteReference" style="font-size: 8pt; ">
                  <note type="footnote" xml:id="_ftn1" n="2">
                     <p rend="FootnoteText"
                        style="margin-left: 0.3333in; text-indent: -0.3333in; font-size: 9pt; hyphenate: false; "
                        xml:lang="en">
                        <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
                        <seg rend="DefaultParagraphFont" style="color: #0070C0; ">A minute on M to J. McCulloch, 30 September 1870 (in this edition as 70-09-30d) instructed M to dismiss according to seniority.</seg>
                     </p>
                  </note>
               </seg>, not every man being able to take an other ones work, special knowledge and experience being in each case requisite. In suggesting, what reductions might be made, I beg respectfully to enquire, whether the men indicated as those, with whose services I can best dispense, might not obtain employment in one of the parks under the board of lands and works or in the railway department.</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">I have the honor to be,</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Sir, your obedient servant</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Ferd. von Mueller</p>
            <p rend="valediction"
               style="font-size: 12pt; margin-left: 1.75in; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>
               <space dim="horizontal" extent="tab"/>Direct. botan Garden</p>
            <space dim="vertical" unit="lines" quantity="1"/>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">The honorable<space unit="chars" quantity="1"/>
            </p>
            <p rend="letter"
               style="font-size: 12pt; hyphenate: false; "
               xml:lang="en">the Chief Secretary</p>
         </div>
